						<summary>

						<p>Stone in the sluice of the tank to the north of the village.</p>						

						<p>Circa 9th century.</p>						

						<p>The record registers a gift of 15 <hi rend="italic">guḷa</hi> of land as <hi rend="italic">ēripaṭṭi,</hi> probably for the upkeep of the sluice caused to be built by Mulagundura Ballamma-seṭṭiti.</p>						

